'''''Mach 3''''' is a [[1987 in video gaming|1987]] 3D [[shoot 'em up]] [[video game]] by [[Loriciels]] for [[Amiga]], [[Amstrad CPC]], [[Atari ST]], [[MSX]], [[Thomson TO7]], [[ZX Spectrum]] and [[DOS]]. The DOS (PC) version uses [[Color Graphics Adapter|CGA]] 320x200 video mode.

== Gameplay ==
The player controls a spacecraft and shoots various enemy crafts while avoiding mines and obstacles. During the intro screen, a sampled is phrase is spoken: "Get ready for Mach 3."

